          "collapsed": "expanded",
          "outputHeight": 88
        },
        "step_intent": "Utilize the Gemini-based text generation agent to create a specific set of instructions for calculating high-precision planetary positions. These instructions will guide the subsequent python execution to use astronomical algorithms (simulating Swiss Ephemeris) based on the location details, date, and time. The output should be a clear, executable set of instructions for a Python script."
