            {
              "text": "Objective: Execute high-precision calculations by generating and running Python code based on the provided instructions. The goal is to produce a structured data set for a Prashna Kundali, specifically detailing planetary positions including Rashi, Nakshatra, and degrees, as well as house cusps.\n\nOutput Format: Provide the resulting structured data set containing the planetary positions and house cusps. Use the generate and execute code tool to perform the calculations in a sandboxed environment. You are done when you have successfully executed the code and returned the structured data using the system objective fulfilled tool.\n\nUser Input / Context: {{\"type\":\"in\",\"path\":\"node_step_python_calculation_instructions\",\"title\":\"Generate Technical Calculation Instructions\"}}"
